data.description: Welcome to 9 Heddin Place in desirable Middletown. Location is key! This 3 bedroom 2.5 bath extended ranch is conveniently located just minutes from restaurants, shopping centers, and direct transpiration to NYC! There are SS appliances throughout the kitchen, a restroom located on each floor, a lot of storage in the attic and basement and skylights that provide natural light in the living room and upstairs bathroom. There's also a bonus room on the second floor for an office or nursery. The backyard includes a large deck with plenty of open space to entertain guests. You do not want to miss out. Make your appointment today!
